Networking Protocols
--------------------
We work using strings between the client and the server. This document outlines the protocols for particular events that may occur during the game.
--------------------

---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------
				ACTION					|				PROTOCOL				|					NOTES
---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------
				IN-GAME					|/////////////////////////////////////	|/////////////////////////////////////
---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------
New co-ordinates when a player moves.	|Move:<x>:<y>										
Angle of player changes.				|
Player gets shot.						|
Bullets firing.							|Bulltet:<x>:<y>:<angle>:<team>
---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|
				GAME STATUS				|/////////////////////////////////////	|
---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|
Win/Loose a game.						|
Change in game points.					|
Game duration.							|
---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|
			CLIENT ACTIONS				|/////////////////////////////////////	|
----------------------------------------|-------------------------------------	|
Join a lobby for a particular game.		|Play:Mode:<game mode>					 1 = TM, 2 = KoTH, 3 = CTF, 4 = ESC
Switch teams.							|SwitchTeam								 Changes from Red->Blue or Blue->Red
Set nickname/username					|Set:Username:<username>
---------------------------------------	|-------------------------------------	|
			CLIENT REQUESTS				|/////////////////////////////////////	|
----------------------------------------|-------------------------------------	|
Get Red team lobby nicknames.			 Get:Red
Get Blue team lobby nicknames.			 Get:Blue
Get nickname.							 Get:Nickname